     <section class="py-24 bg-white" id="about">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
       <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="reveal">
         <h2 class="text-sm font-bold text-red-600 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">
          O M&eacute;todo
         </h2>
         <h3 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-zinc-900 mb-8 tracking-tighter leading-tight">
          55 MINUTOS.
          <br>
          DOIS
          <span class="text-zinc-400 italic">
           BLOCOS.
          </span>
          UM RESULTADO.
         </h3>
         <div class="space-y-6 text-zinc-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <p>
           O treino da Insanus Fight tem 55 minutos de intensidade real, divididos em dois blocos. No primeiro, trabalho funcional com el&aacute;sticos, halteres, caneleiras e, acima de tudo, o peso do pr&oacute;prio corpo. No segundo, muay thai: s&eacute;ries de chutes, socos, joelhadas e cotoveladas em ritmo alto.
          </p>
          <p>
           A soma dos dois blocos entrega o que treino isolado n&atilde;o entrega: gasto cal&oacute;rico elevado, condicionamento que se sustenta e t&eacute;cnica de luta aprendida do jeito certo, desde o primeiro dia. N&atilde;o importa se voc&ecirc; nunca cal&ccedil;ou uma luva &mdash; a aula se ajusta ao seu n&iacute;vel.
          </p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 pt-6">
           <div class="bg-zinc-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-zinc-100 hover:border-red-100 hover:bg-red-50/30 transition-all group reveal">
            <div class="bg-white w-10 h-10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm mb-4 group-hover:bg-red-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
             <svg aria-hidden="true" class="lucide lucide-target" fill="none" height="20" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" viewbox="0 0 24 24" width="20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10">
              </circle>
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6">
              </circle>
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2">
              </circle>
             </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-zinc-900 text-lg mb-2">
             Objetivo Claro
            </h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed">
             Cada aluno treina com uma meta definida, e o coach ajusta a carga para ela.
            </p>
           </div>
           <div class="bg-zinc-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-zinc-100 hover:border-red-100 hover:bg-red-50/30 transition-all group reveal">
            <div class="bg-white w-10 h-10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm mb-4 group-hover:bg-red-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
             <svg aria-hidden="true" class="lucide lucide-shield" fill="none" height="20" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" viewbox="0 0 24 24" width="20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z">
              </path>
             </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-zinc-900 text-lg mb-2">
             Defesa Pessoal
            </h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed">
             Golpes de muay thai ensinados com aplica&ccedil;&atilde;o real, n&atilde;o s&oacute; como exerc&iacute;cio.
            </p>
           </div>
           <div class="bg-zinc-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-zinc-100 hover:border-red-100 hover:bg-red-50/30 transition-all group reveal">
            <div class="bg-white w-10 h-10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm mb-4 group-hover:bg-red-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
             <svg aria-hidden="true" class="lucide lucide-users" fill="none" height="20" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" viewbox="0 0 24 24" width="20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2">
              </path>
              <path d="M16 3.128a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.744">
              </path>
              <path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87">
              </path>
              <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4">
              </circle>
             </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-zinc-900 text-lg mb-2">
             Turmas Reduzidas
            </h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed">
             No m&aacute;ximo 8 alunos por aula coletiva. Todo mundo recebe corre&ccedil;&atilde;o.
            </p>
           </div>
           <div class="bg-zinc-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-zinc-100 hover:border-red-100 hover:bg-red-50/30 transition-all group reveal">
            <div class="bg-white w-10 h-10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm mb-4 group-hover:bg-red-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
             <svg aria-hidden="true" class="lucide lucide-trending-up" fill="none" height="20" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" viewbox="0 0 24 24" width="20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M16 7h6v6">
              </path>
              <path d="m22 7-8.5 8.5-5-5L2 17">
              </path>
             </svg>
